    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hi @Haroenv .\r\nWhat do you mean with use float values?\r\nSomething like this:\r\n\r\n```\r\n    [\r\n        { label: 'Max Kms' },\r\n        { label: '9,999 or less', start: 1.0, end: 9999.0 },\r\n        { label: '19,999', start: 1.0, end: 19999.0 },\r\n        { label: '34,999', start: 1.0, end: 34999.0 },\r\n        { label: '44,999', start: 1.0, end: 44999.0 },\r\n        { label: '54,999', start: 1.0, end: 54999.0 },\r\n        { label: '99,999', start: 1.0, end: 99999.0 },\r\n        { label: 'Over 100,000', start: 100000 },\r\n    ]\r\n```\r\n\r\nneither does it work.",
